    {
      "id": "label-31cd97d5-ce78-4685-a398-31798f52a503",
      "name": "book1_block_day1_alt_predator_core",
      "x": 25300,
      "y": 1942.5,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-9994aab9-f08b-4511-a078-b325955afa46",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-0ccd5e67-4329-42e6-ae5e-5b3a1240a35e",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-bdbff822-1fb5-4688-bf4c-2bf95fdc42b6",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "type": "if_block",
          "branches": [
            {
              "id": "3b2ba532-8f60-419b-98cb-681e04cb1ff0",
              "type": "if",
              "conditionRaw": "story.missy_day1_trust_state == \"unsettled\"",
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "id": "item-9b3f02c6-1468-4ad5-944a-377920a43930",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-7ab97087-249f-4c1e-a484-7c707d4a6864",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-76e09b42-a273-4132-bc7d-96b9e7e2b074",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-31435fde-524b-429a-ac0b-3e01cbcf6ee8",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "In the Savoy, I had seen Missy's trust curdle in a single afternoon. I wrote it as Miri's fear—thicker than the jasmine, sweeter than the rot. The manuscript demanded blood before it demanded beauty."
                }
              ],
              "condition": {
                "operator": "and",
                "clauses": []
              },
              "rawCondition": "story.missy_day1_trust_state == \"unsettled\""
            },
            {
              "id": "cec56335-cde6-43fb-a3c2-52412bb52032",
              "type": "else",
              "conditionRaw": null,
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "id": "item-6fb24df9-a1c5-42a0-b22f-1b2f0e5ce8c5",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-ab26a17f-bcdf-4719-af3b-f87e45ec36b0",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-82119f66-37d8-4c02-993b-8a9198583671",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-da1f5f11-9443-43f6-bfca-c9e37add92ed",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "I wrote Miri's hand on my sleeve as a bond. In the real hotel, Missy had clutched my arm during the corridor inspection, and I had used her fear as a pass. The page demands I admit I was grateful for the heat of it, even if I could not afford to return it."
                }
              ],
              "condition": {
                "operator": "and",
                "clauses": []
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "item-06c73ae6-af0b-4b36-9d76-a40e4f65688b"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-c327a961-ae02-4043-9b5b-f0852ea24eef",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "type": "if_block",
          "branches": [
            {
              "id": "2511ec97-1897-47b4-a162-e7ba4363af04",
              "type": "if",
              "conditionRaw": "story.day1_interview_state == \"meek\"",
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "id": "item-9db83177-4846-4909-90c9-d091252fab53",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-5d62dc4f-2a71-4083-acd7-ddcf91a7b11b",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-5f89753e-4e26-4361-8aaa-fb0496d44d91",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-f7bb12bd-7877-4f44-8eb9-5a6f2691c7ed",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "In the Savoy, I had played the fool for Ms. Stern. It bought me three days of invisibility. On the page, I let Coralie do the same—a stitched golem of cotton and lye, dancing for a master who would never see the strings I cut."
                }
              ],
              "condition": {
                "operator": "and",
                "clauses": []
              },
              "rawCondition": "story.day1_interview_state == \"meek\""
            },
            {
              "id": "c667019e-cde8-4dac-949c-88d063c40a66",
              "type": "elif",
              "conditionRaw": "story.day1_interview_state == \"competent\"",
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "id": "item-854c8b52-ef29-4c96-8dfe-4f9f5815032d",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-ef3aa97e-e769-4775-a807-185b215c2e63",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-88358985-baa1-40f8-903d-71f3ed904752",
                  "type": "call",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-67d99592-323d-49a0-afa9-6dd46d55a37d",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "Ms. Stern had respected the efficient mask. I wrote Sterick as a man who saw through it and chose not to speak. The cold understanding between us was the engine that kept the story turning."
                }
              ],
              "condition": {
                "operator": "and",
                "clauses": []
              },
              "rawCondition": "story.day1_interview_state == \"competent\""
            }
          ],
          "id": "item-5fbabea2-b5cf-4dbf-b1a6-f00262343010"
        },
        {
          "type": "if_block",
          "branches": [
            {
              "id": "98de7c26-0e6f-4120-808f-61599fe0a994",
              "type": "if",
