        {
          "id": "item-a282a4d4-8df7-4d56-a949-4e1703fc438c",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-7088822b-393e-42e5-a65d-6848c2278069",
          "type": "call",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-dcfd45f7-9541-4117-ba4c-61e52b94e96b"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-bd26b2f7-af47-4797-8104-2027de748f69",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "In the real hotel, I lacked the claws. I was just a girl with a forged accent and a stolen ledger. But the page demands a bolder blood."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-188d7fbe-c6c2-40b1-a8ed-6ebf1d604c5d",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "So I sharpened my nib. And I wrote myself into a monster."
        },
        {
          "type": "if_block",
          "branches": [
            {
              "id": "87118d50-f2b1-40a7-8610-d6f1081eda3b",
