    {
      "id": "label-3d60d0f2-d23a-4d17-a419-06cc0cd80ae0",
      "name": "day100_main",
      "x": 900,
      "y": 11885,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "type": "python_script",
          "code": "set_time_period(\"Night\")",
          "id": "item-5d18e838-bb9b-4eef-8cf7-a56e6c034cb8"
        },
        {
          "type": "scene",
          "layer": null,
          "transition": "None",
          "id": "item-d0286cf7-8b52-491e-be6a-84d4631fe1af",
          "backgroundId": "bg_country_estate_corridor_night"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-429ff039-6d83-4ccb-a5a2-5a14e957846c",
          "type": "show",
          "characterId": "cora_sprite",
          "isFlipped": false,
          "xpos": 0.5,
          "ypos": 1,
          "zoom": 1,
          "alpha": 1,
          "transition": "moveinright",
          "layer": null,
          "atlBlocks": [],
          "spriteId": "cora_sprite base"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-5d89da09-2de0-4937-9885-f2e1e49bd200",
          "type": "show",
          "characterId": "cora_sprite",
          "isFlipped": false,
          "xpos": 0.5,
          "ypos": 1,
          "zoom": 1,
          "alpha": 1,
          "transition": "",
          "layer": null,
          "atlBlocks": [],
          "spriteId": "cora_sprite base"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-85ae9b49-4b54-459e-b2b1-473e60dce80e",
          "type": "show",
          "characterId": "vance_sprite",
          "isFlipped": false,
          "xpos": 0.1,
          "ypos": 1,
          "zoom": 1,
          "alpha": 1,
          "transition": "",
          "layer": null,
          "atlBlocks": [],
          "spriteId": "vance_sprite base"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-d2703b5c-8ffc-4c91-8d37-324370a1d1e1",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Cora had three pages in her hand when the door opened."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-d0757399-1591-474a-8217-da5ac884cb4a",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "She blew out the candle too late."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-4f0c92fc-ca3d-4964-85fe-8dec2ec62941",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Wiltshire at night is a cold vault, but my chest is tight and hot."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-1ad2e4af-ffd6-4dd8-828b-423c45efa66e",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "I keep my boots in my left hand, the rough wool of my stockings catching on the bare floorboards."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-621b3524-bc07-48be-8e88-1e66303792db",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "I know every riser that groans, every latch that clicks — the map a fugitive maid learns."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-8f016409-9f1e-4368-9a5a-b63b99bcb464",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "My secret manuscript pages are pressed flat against my ribs, hidden under my bodice."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-b1499d40-642b-41bc-9deb-df19391b184b",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "But three pages are missing. Confiscated. Snatched from my trunk while I scrubbed the grates."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-849f92aa-5676-4791-80bf-887c5de8d38e",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "A grandfather clock tolls three. The vibration runs through the floorboards like a warning."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-fb628925-3e45-4f01-8764-15f26d072bd2",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "In my head the words come soft, looping — my mother's Cork lilt. I swallow it whole."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-1e79db47-c513-450b-92d5-832f5beec251",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Out loud I must be flat. English. Sterile. One slip and I am Irish street-grub, not Vale the maid."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-eee42e0c-b5d1-42c8-89b1-92b4791fa163",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "A floorboard creaks downstairs. I freeze, my breath catching in my throat."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-835a956f-6a6d-4e6a-8bc5-f5ef2f0e5e3d",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "I wait in the clock's shadow, counting heartbeats until the house resets to silence."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-609f2808-e9d7-453f-8543-5579742ddac1",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "I am terrified, but I am in control."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-88be82af-bfde-403e-ae1b-ae6f16b2c995",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Wiltshire has no room for a maid who writes. To they who rule, a maid is wallpaper that walks."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-794c14a2-9905-44a4-86a4-9918cb100429",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "If the Lady read those pages, she will have me stripped and searched. If Sir John reads them, I am unmasked."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-221c4cd9-9dd2-444e-98f2-efc112353c15",
          "type": "jump",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-ee16379a-613b-419b-80bc-2b912bf46ede"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-ee16379a-613b-419b-80bc-2b912bf46ede",
      "name": "day100_1_afternoon_boredom_setup",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 11885,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-5f1ed496-754c-45a5-abc8-f121a8fdad31",
          "type": "jump",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-2f0aa2bc-294c-4efb-a791-1a0e7dbac6a7"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-2f0aa2bc-294c-4efb-a791-1a0e7dbac6a7",
      "name": "day100_1_afternoon_boredom",
      "x": 1700,
      "y": 11885,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "type": "scene",
          "layer": null,
          "transition": "None",
          "id": "item-097113b2-7ded-473f-8a55-2be9a60361bd",
          "backgroundId": "bg_country_estate_study"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-b13f41ca-1120-4076-8a0f-7b8620747de5",
          "type": "show",
          "characterId": "cora_sprite",
          "isFlipped": false,
          "xpos": 0.5,
          "ypos": 1,
          "zoom": 1,
          "alpha": 1,
          "transition": "moveinright",
          "layer": null,
          "atlBlocks": [],
          "spriteId": "cora_sprite base"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-445bef76-aa82-42e1-938a-19b7c5e57cf0",
          "type": "show",
          "characterId": "cora_sprite",
          "isFlipped": false,
          "xpos": 0.5,
          "ypos": 1,
          "zoom": 1,
          "alpha": 1,
          "transition": "",
          "layer": null,
          "atlBlocks": [],
          "spriteId": "cora_sprite guarded_travel"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-e3f97363-a817-4dd4-83e7-529242dd6777",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Lady Eleanor's withdrawing room. The door stands open by a finger's width."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-b12e7880-a6c8-4f9c-a8e5-6c0a2a1036b6",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "It smells of costly amber, lavender-water, and the wet coal-smog leaking from the hearth."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-8dd1d69f-95dd-4a21-9271-57fd5b544a7c",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "I must find my pages before the morning train. They hold appetite dressed as literature."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-518c9919-e935-4e8f-9401-10c6f17bcb88",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": null,
          "text": "Where would Eleanor Wiltshire hide evidence of a servant's transgressive imagination?"
        },
        {
          "type": "choice",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "6b59ecdf-1108-43d9-89fa-c818bcd62354",
              "text": "In the walnut bureau drawer. [[Search the bureau: Careful, corrupting]]",
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "type": "python_script",
                  "code": "apply_balanced_effect(\"creative\", intensity=\"standard\")",
                  "id": "item-8cb73144-ebd5-4f86-b48d-b9f435f53a32"
                },
                {
                  "type": "python_script",
                  "code": "story.set_prologue_found(\"read_letters\")",
                  "id": "item-73f62171-c7a5-4553-920a-23d9d9a3da14"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-59615b72-cf42-4faf-8472-9496722ea8f2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "The bureau is where she locks the letters that make her hands tremble."
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-33d6fa82-9842-4b66-a122-86a046600b68",
                  "type": "jump",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-4912916d-8e3d-4d67-a4bd-4bad8a92744b"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "38ba67ce-c3e9-4f9d-92dc-8a34182fac9e",
              "text": "By the private parlour settee. [[Search the parlour entrance: Transgressive]]",
              "dialogue": [
                {
                  "type": "python_script",
                  "code": "apply_balanced_effect(\"creative\", intensity=\"standard\")",
                  "id": "item-a45e3fb9-66b1-4012-9b8d-363d1f924501"
                },
                {
                  "type": "python_script",
                  "code": "story.set_prologue_found(\"overheard\")",
                  "id": "item-e55259da-eb7e-4155-b714-24349dbed666"
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-c26a8447-73d3-4154-9df0-85f920f902bc",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "characterId": null,
                  "text": "The small parlour. A muffled gasp slips from behind the heavy velvet drapes."
                },
                {
                  "id": "item-f4c66cdc-ad02-46fa-ab85-0605fea201d7",
                  "type": "jump",
                  "destinationLabelId": "label-4912916d-8e3d-4d67-a4bd-4bad8a92744b"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "item-f1a646cb-88b1-4a06-ac9e-5b3ac5421df2"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-02960be1-9287-4a16-8e82-7e3329598c47",
          "type": "jump",
          "destinationLabelId": "label-4912916d-8e3d-4d67-a4bd-4bad8a92744b"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-4912916d-8e3d-4d67-a4bd-4bad8a92744b",
