    {
      "id": "label-41dcf941-29cf-4536-9067-5c09ef037338",
      "name": "game_over_dismissed",
      "x": 22900,
      "y": 11997.5,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-f97a51c2-36eb-4da3-a698-e51ccabe9349",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "═══ GAME OVER: NERVOUS BREAKDOWN ═══"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-c106b22e-20f2-46b5-9a15-fa87d1bdcb94",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I could not keep the walls of my mind standing."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-98c37660-827d-43bd-aa3a-080e78383b63",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "It was not a single eye that caught me. It was the weight of them all."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-3b84cb5f-f19c-45dc-9cbf-3bba23b8ce57",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "Vance's sharp contempt, Missy's mounting fear, Stern's cold, measuring gaze... they accumulated in my chest like lead."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-fdc52e50-4f77-47f4-9dc8-6054cae64876",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "The weight of their combined eyes cracks my mask."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-3c517429-ea08-4043-97c6-2b4a5883867c",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I made a fatal slip in my duties, and Miss Stern found absolute cause to dismiss me."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-226976a0-81c8-4da8-b2f9-19662a28274e",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-73fd1dc9-64b4-4025-9914-bd03daa1de46",
          "text": "Pack your things. A girl whose nerves are in such tatters cannot be trusted with the Savoy's quiet."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-f4577d70-aaba-4fe7-a3f5-1089a309e18b",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "My hands were shaking too hard to tie my trunk. I stood on the Strand with nothing but a ruined reputation and the memory of electric light."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-81cded5e-1ba6-446d-a541-288dc0d116eb",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "Without a character, London is a very cold, very hungry place."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-aa7fc7b8-1e6e-4764-8d7d-1689558509e2",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "[[GAME OVER. Your accumulated Anxiety reached 100%%, causing a complete breakdown and leading to your dismissal. Manage your internal strain by spreading suspicion across different characters and triggering penances before your nerves fail you.]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-1776c6e9-dbce-4e73-855b-df61bbd09d45",
      "name": "bad_ending_rejection",
      "x": 25300,
      "y": 11290,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-381b253b-7d64-447c-8054-0b4e071a9f26",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "═══ BAD ENDING: REJECTION ═══"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-dbe96a7f-d5b2-44fb-af1f-6cb8d477d50c",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I sat at the desk. I wrote. I wrote for hours."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-e6ed1cb4-9289-4853-aee3-726543e1faaf",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "But the words that came out were... safe. Polite. Bloodless."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-656cc646-4459-44cf-9f56-dc50d40d027c",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "A schoolgirl's fairy tale dressed in a corset. All the right shapes, none of the heat."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-84ea86ed-c714-41c1-bcb6-50c69e0b8d21",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I sent it to Holywell Street anyway. What else could I do?"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-e0b0d1f7-36d0-4314-9e80-6435a9ad90a0",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "The errand boy returned my manuscript the next morning. Unopened. A note was pinned to the front."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-10ec7ca2-1917-41ff-9096-66995a434c80",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "'We asked for fire. You sent us porridge.'"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-ca699814-b648-4438-848e-5256503b63a4",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I stared at the note for a long time."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-26e0ca52-27b4-41b8-a6d0-2b9c4e0e16ee",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I am not brave enough. Not worldly enough. Not ruined enough to write what they need."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-08d454b5-c284-4124-80ba-70d8ffc121f7",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I will scrub floors until my hands are raw and my stories die inside me. I will send seven shillings home every month. I will be a good girl."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-ae8e9366-d789-4a21-844c-f9527ccf2d76",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "And no one will ever read a single word I've written."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-8edd78a0-3a19-41be-a801-0ed353f6a093",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "[[BAD ENDING. You survived — but at the cost of your dream. The 'Pure' path is safe, but it is a cage. Try again, and this time, look through the grate.]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-86bf649c-fdbf-4350-910e-a5ec2e9fd61c",
      "name": "game_over_deadline_1",
      "x": 12900,
      "y": 12147.5,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-4d8a1483-b6e7-41e0-9fee-4f3a3e06e79c",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "═══ GAME OVER: FIRST DEADLINE FAILED ═══"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-157e88cf-a723-4b64-ba75-d106e8d8beba",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I stare at the blank page."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-00d7d4bf-fae4-4b6a-b424-3621368ac3f4",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "Day 2 has ended, and I have not even written the first chapter."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-26aeec79-bebd-4e48-9a4a-1c9612688420",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "Without a single page of progress, my ambition is nothing but a childish delusion."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-2222fe64-7b22-4559-a55e-ddb25bb23961",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I cannot face the publisher. I cannot face the page."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-1af4a7f2-9185-42d9-a2b1-a0f1e23f022d",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I have failed before I even truly began."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-7ced26b5-1cf4-4d4b-b1b3-158371a0916f",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "[[GAME OVER. You failed to write Chapter 1 by Day 2 Night. Manage your time and stats to ensure you have enough inspiration to write.]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-8cfac59a-d4f9-4532-82a9-c0ca8c0e7ee8",
      "name": "game_over_deadline_2",
      "x": 22500,
      "y": 11252.5,
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "id": "item-090da7fd-7230-4d3a-be65-92dbca92eaae",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "═══ GAME OVER: DRAFT DEADLINE FAILED ═══"
        },
        {
          "id": "item-d51ff3f7-93dc-4fa4-9778-709624a570bd",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "The night of Day 4 passes into grey dawn."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-c51d9f5b-ade8-4527-a8ea-8298e9bf8429",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "My desk is littered with scraps of paper, but the draft is incomplete. I have only one chapter done."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-1f256d7c-3655-4f8c-bd1f-be664a1a2b04",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "The publisher's courier will arrive tomorrow. I have nothing to give him but excuses."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-867868e3-7bd4-4c75-8647-f61c944dc3f5",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-46d27e95-f9db-4406-aabf-f20f0316869c",
          "text": "I have lost my chance. The door is closed."
        },
        {
          "id": "item-766cdda3-2528-4015-8ac7-84a6971c81b5",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "characterId": "char-57d70705-3dd2-4564-893b-e1358b867691",
          "text": "[[GAME OVER. You failed to complete a second chapter/draft by Day 4 Night. Balance your stats and avoid confrontations to protect your writing slots!]"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "label-5f635f30-8ef3-4f17-80e7-4e5cde552ded",
